Main conclusion: the first usable ASMS home shell depends on Metro config hydration during login bootstrap via PHP `RestClient` to `http://127.0.0.1:8080/afa`; Apache’s external equivalent is `/afa/api/v1/config`, while `/afa/config` is not externally mapped on this appliance and was observed returning `404`.
